title: Navigating the rocky road to European tech sovereignty at the Tech.eu Summit - Tech.eu
content: Navigating the rocky road to European tech sovereignty at the Tech.eu Summit  Tech.eu
description: Join Scaleway chief exec Yann Lechelle, Box's EMEA president Sebastien Marotte, and Veriff co-founder Janer Gorohhov at the Tech.eu Summit as they unpack Europe's tech sovereignty ambitions.
